address2: No. 108, Huangpu Avenue West Tianhe District
longBusinessSummary: China Aoyuan Group Limited engages in the development of real estate properties primarily in Mainland China, Australia, and Canada. The company operates through Property Development, Property Investment, and Others segments. It also develops, leases, and sells various real estate projects; and operates cultural tourism, and hotel operation. In addition, the company manufactures chemical and fiber products; and sale of goods and provision of services. Further, it provides construction and design; property management services; consultancy services; and loan financing services. The company was formerly known as China Aoyuan Property Group Limited and changed its name to China Aoyuan Group Limited in November 2018. China Aoyuan Group Limited was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Guangzhou, the People's Republic of China. China Aoyuan Group Limited operates as a subsidiary of Ace Rise Profits Limited.
